RAWALPINDI, Jun 22 (APP):Chief of Army Staff (COAS) General Qamar Javed Bajwa Monday expressed grief on the demise of renowned religious scholar, Allama Talib Jauhari.
According to the Inter Services Public Relations (ISPR) the COAS said, “May Allah bless the departed soul in eternal peace and give strength to the bereaved family, Aameen.”
